commit.message:
Circumvent problems of Qt stylesheet in kvantum theme (#64)

This simple change is a workaround for 3 bugs of Qt stylesheet, revealed by kvantum theme: (1) selected menu arrows weren't shown; (2) taskbar right-click (sub)menus didn't have enough width; and (3) selected check-boxes could have a weird border, sometimes when checked, sometimes when unchecked.

Those problems don't show up in most themes because they include the workarounds automatically.

verification.payload:
tree bf153ca5454e439cf445af6187631d003551b25a
parent 4d7dd3687a04d71569718f7f170d74d176d0013b
author tsujan <tsujan2000@gmail.com> 1649334539 +0430
committer GitHub <noreply@github.com> 1649334539 +0430

Circumvent problems of Qt stylesheet in kvantum theme (#64)

This simple change is a workaround for 3 bugs of Qt stylesheet, revealed by kvantum theme: (1) selected menu arrows weren't shown; (2) taskbar right-click (sub)menus didn't have enough width; and (3) selected check-boxes could have a weird border, sometimes when checked, sometimes when unchecked.

Those problems don't show up in most themes because they include the workarounds automatically.
